{"tid":1766291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉：僅關注法案制裁名單眼光短淺  當中有條文可能會阻礙粵港澳大灣區發展","createTime":"2019-12-02T12:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T13:09:01.000Z","uid":133680,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc843e193783112894659bc2ba5221e8118d9e7","tid":1766291,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:48:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3599445306762732/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F139543009419663%2Fposts%2F3599445306762732%2F&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwReDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=c6a7aa9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3599445306762732/</a><br />\n【Solomon's「best friend」發言】葉劉：僅關注法案制裁名單眼光短淺 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2LdsR2t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LdsR2t&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwReDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=2ce305b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2LdsR2t</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統 #特朗普 早前簽署《#香港人權與民主法案》，在立法會財經事務委員會上，新民黨 #葉劉淑儀 關注法案對香港的實際影響。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，當中有條文可能會阻礙粵港澳大灣區發展<del></del>，對香港造成傷害更大。財政司司長 #陳茂波 認同法案影響香港創新科技以及大灣區發展，但他拒進一步評論法案的影響，指周五在立法會將召開聯合委員會集中討論。<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n「反修例風暴」新聞專題 深入分析<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2l1PLjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2l1PLjs&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwReDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=11245d99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2l1PLjs</a><br />\n<br />\n#信報 #即時新聞 #新民黨 #反修例風波 #美國總統"},{"pid":"e1a302fa3ed820f14206acff9959232e183ff136","tid":1766291,"uid":185022,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"係就最好啦<br />\n大灣區關我地撚事咩"},{"pid":"e51bde208c08bae1c8098bc5d5b5df1554f3ac13","tid":1766291,"uid":300006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:51:52.000Z","msg":"姐姐，你好撚煩。<br />\n你唔提法案無人會再拎你黎講架，靜啦。"},{"pid":"c3b51e